Maintainer: Guilherme D. Garcia <guilherme.garcia@lli.ulaval.ca>
Description: A collection of tools to help with phonological analysis. Functions include grapheme to phoneme conversion, sonority dispersion calculation, minimal matrices for natural classes given a set of features, maxent models, and more.
